    <item>
      <title>卢比奥会见总统后巴拿马向美国做出让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥周日访问中国期间对巴拿马政府进行猛烈批评后，巴拿马承诺让美国军舰自由通过巴拿马运河，并表示将退出中国签署的贷款计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 19:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对中国征收 10% 关税后，习近平考虑采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发动新一轮贸易战后，加拿大和墨西哥领导人迅速作出回应，而中国国家主席习近平则在宣布具体反击措施之前稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/xi-weighs-retaliation-after-trump-hits-china-with-10-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普瞄准漏洞 Temu，Shein 曾与亚马逊较量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收的新贸易税包括对国际电子商务的猛烈攻击，显然是计划取消长期以来对价值低于 800 美元的包裹的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</guid>
